<title>JAPAN: Mitsubishi Motor shares fall on loss news.</title>
<headline>Mitsubishi Motor shares fall on loss news.</headline>
<dateline>TOKYO 1997-04-28</dateline>
<text>
<p>Shares in Mitsubishi Motor Corp fell sharply on Monday morning, after the firm announced on Friday it would post an appraisal loss of 43.1 billion yen on securities holdings in the year to March 1997.</p>
<p>At 0130 GMT, the share price was down 30 yen at 880 yen. Trading volume was 1.538 million shares, making it the fifth most heavily traded issue on the first section of the Tokyo Stock Exchange.</p>
